00:25:22.170 --> 00:25:24.030
but people aren't debating
about, oh, let's do this

00:25:24.030 --> 00:25:25.500
or that for a long
period of time.

00:25:25.500 --> 00:25:27.167
So, there's also when
you're there, just

00:25:27.167 --> 00:25:28.930
focusing on doing the work.

00:25:28.930 --> 00:25:32.010
So, those are some of
the characteristics

00:25:32.010 --> 00:25:33.630
of this great group
in Menlo Park.

