00:27:17.410 --> 00:27:22.460
And on the island bridge
point that Martin made,

00:27:22.460 --> 00:27:27.590
a key set of relationships
that Edison was able to form

00:27:27.590 --> 00:27:31.860
was that telegraphing in
effect like quadruplexing

00:27:31.860 --> 00:27:32.820
by telegraph.

00:27:32.820 --> 00:27:36.510
The ability to send multiple
messages over the same line.

00:27:36.510 --> 00:27:40.290
That really enables the stock
ticker and a tremendous amount

00:27:40.290 --> 00:27:42.900
of exchange of financial
information for stock

00:27:42.900 --> 00:27:44.190
exchanges.

00:27:44.190 --> 00:27:46.770
So, buying could
occur at a distance.

00:27:46.770 --> 00:27:49.080
You could place orders from
all over the country, which

00:27:49.080 --> 00:27:51.690
really is foundational
for Wall Street.

00:27:51.690 --> 00:27:54.300
So, people like JP Morgan
completely understood

00:27:54.300 --> 00:27:57.630
the power of this and have
a relationship with Edison.

00:27:57.630 --> 00:28:01.110
So, the Edison crowd is
all off in this rural farm

00:28:01.110 --> 00:28:05.910
on an island, but Edison has
got a bridge back to JP Morgan.

00:28:05.910 --> 00:28:10.360
So, when they figure out the
light bulb, and the system that

00:28:10.360 --> 00:28:14.190
goes with it, which
I'll get to in a second,

00:28:14.190 --> 00:28:17.100
he's got a way to reach a
decision maker who can actually

00:28:17.100 --> 00:28:18.910
stand up to technology.

00:28:18.910 --> 00:28:19.410
Right.

00:28:19.410 --> 00:28:20.760
And that's really crucial.

00:28:20.760 --> 00:28:23.850
So, that invention earlier
that he came up with

00:28:23.850 --> 00:28:27.180
is really the enabler
for this whole project.

00:28:27.180 --> 00:28:29.610
They have to ship
because, as Martin says,

00:28:29.610 --> 00:28:32.130
they've got a limited amount
of money, which they're burning

00:28:32.130 --> 00:28:36.090
through by purchasing every
bizarre thing you can think of,

00:28:36.090 --> 00:28:40.130
as you just ran through
the great list of.

00:28:40.130 --> 00:28:42.767
So, it's driven by
the need to ship.

00:28:42.767 --> 00:28:44.600
They're going to have
to get this thing done

00:28:44.600 --> 00:28:47.160
before their money runs out.

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:51.080
So, they're working all hours
with incredible intensity

00:28:51.080 --> 00:28:53.400
to try and do it.

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:57.290
This is not just the
invention of the light bulb.

00:28:57.290 --> 00:28:58.730
They have to invent--

00:28:58.730 --> 00:29:01.910
a light bulb is worthless
without an electrical system

00:29:01.910 --> 00:29:03.330
to go with it.

00:29:03.330 --> 00:29:05.810
So, one of the things
that Edison and his crew

00:29:05.810 --> 00:29:08.420
figure out they
essentially have to invent

00:29:08.420 --> 00:29:10.865
the entire public utility model.

00:29:10.865 --> 00:29:12.740
So, they got a light
bulb, which is a useless

00:29:12.740 --> 00:29:16.400
product unless you have an
electrical system go with it.

00:29:16.400 --> 00:29:20.233
So, they have to think
through power systems.

00:29:20.233 --> 00:29:21.650
They have to think
through safety.

00:29:21.650 --> 00:29:23.750
They have to figure
out generators.

00:29:23.750 --> 00:29:26.090
They have to figure out
the organizational model

00:29:26.090 --> 00:29:29.132
for utilities in order to
understand how this whole thing

00:29:29.132 --> 00:29:29.840
is going to work.

00:29:29.840 --> 00:29:33.200
So, they've got a
dream product that's

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:36.110
going to displace, you know, gas
lighting, which was incredibly

00:29:36.110 --> 00:29:42.080
dangerous, blew up all the time,
with a much safer, inherently

00:29:42.080 --> 00:29:46.005
safer system, which provided
much better quality light.

00:29:46.005 --> 00:29:47.630
So, they've got a
dream product, but it

00:29:47.630 --> 00:29:51.170
doesn't work unless they
do the entire innovation

00:29:51.170 --> 00:29:54.080
system for electricity along
with it, which is really

00:29:54.080 --> 00:29:56.050
what their accomplishment is.

00:29:56.050 --> 00:29:56.575
Right.

00:29:56.575 --> 00:29:58.700
It's understanding and
being able to put into place

00:29:58.700 --> 00:30:01.820
the whole system, and then
using their bridge back

00:30:01.820 --> 00:30:04.820
to the financial world
to get it financed.

00:30:04.820 --> 00:30:08.270
So, those are just a few points
building on Martin's, you know,

00:30:08.270 --> 00:30:11.140
